A comic book style illustration of two figures on opposite planets in space - one planet is red (Mars) with a stressed designer hunched over a glowing computer screen surrounded by floating wireframes and mockups, the other planet is yellow-orange (Venus) with a confused customer gesturing wildly at a tablet, scratching their head. Between them floats a tangled mess of colorful speech bubbles and question marks connecting the two worlds. The scene uses bold outlines, halftone dots, and vibrant pop art colors with dramatic shading. The cosmic background features stars and nebulae in deep purples and blues, emphasizing the vast communication gap between the two characters.
